Strong tides have been flowing through me night and day, and I seem to be living all through me now. It's rather more than mere physical exercise that does it. 
Bovard asked me if I thought I might be able to interest a publisher in those articles he showed me x
I'll try, of course. 
I do want to pay the god's ransom, as that was the plan. 
Endless love to you both. 
Dad 
